16 • Beaverton

Role in Story
Provide insight into life in Beaverton, the role of Beaveroon committees and whatnot in shaping the destiny of the Lands. Brings a technical angle into the plot lines regarding flight, in particular.

Goal
My goal: Provide for an (angsty) teenage hero in the story!  Internal goal:  create a thread connecting the Jaxen/Created to the main storylines, other than as an “evil other”.  

